Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(康斯肯的强袭)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前，曾经是\N卫星一号的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，却成了萨比家中将
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所指挥的宇宙攻击总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙要塞-所罗门基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里，康斯肯的部队\N刚刚出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德兹尔中将对姊姊希莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次任用夏亚\N感到非常的反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很想自己来击沉母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,籍以证明夏亚的无能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他们仍未查明\N帝姆舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去月神二号的目的前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不能派遗\N太多兵力去别处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你觉得怎样？\N有不妥当吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看应是没问题的\N不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这附近有很多岩石\N便很难说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯，你听到吗？怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切正常\N不过我不能长途飞行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想G战机再巡一次\N可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那对我来说\N可以做多些飞行练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？阿姆罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为芙劳‧波的为人怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？为何你会这样问？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你最近对她很冷淡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有这种事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为这时最重要是友谊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我没有\N说过讨厌她呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敌军！         咦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照情况看是被发现了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，再等一会吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不是故障\N不会被发现的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎没问题吧！   没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，雪拉快闪开！   咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们开火了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吉翁的机动堡垒吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...还是未知道的！\N又来了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理，为何开火啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他们想攻击我们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.52,0:04:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们根本\N就没有攻击的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太没胆了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！这架战机看来很快速！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们分开作战\N快闪到岩石后！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们将电力加得太高了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法了\N既然已暴露了行踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有拚死一战了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3...2...1...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一架战机\N不用怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以很高速攻过来了\N小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们到底\N从那里攻击过来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是多方向呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.73,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么辛苦才修理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，很久了\N进入卫星六号前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先返回母舰吧！   知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这灯塔后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是卫星六号领空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是联邦或吉翁也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一律是被禁止\N在这里开战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是卫星六号的检查官\N卡姆兰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经在母舰的\N导弹发射口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大炮，雷射炮\N用这样封条封好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既使你们弄破了一条\N也知道的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.09,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，会罚巨款是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想修理母舰\N可以帮忙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这...也不可以\N在卫星内进行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这等于协助战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我带你控制室看看\N好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.34,0:07:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呢，雪拉\N我明明看得清彻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那炮火不是在\N战机的方向射过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不会看错的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未查出原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看那是新型的机动堡垒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能的         是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来得刚好\N我们正要入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入港角度好，速度0.5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在进入卫星六号\N巴达港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请各位做好准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,角度360
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开所有雷射调整器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱？你不是米莱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰，是你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，你没有事\N真太好了...米莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看来很精神，你好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是谁？         或许是亲人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰检察官\N现在正要入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以待会再说吗？\N米莱少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...中尉，对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为再见不到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以为没希望了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全因为你父亲过世后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则便不会有战争了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，否则\N我也不会去移民去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 7里，逃避事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么不通知我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想得到你的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经尽力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽了力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀！我着人四处去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用尽了所有的金钱！\N是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...为何你\N不自己来找呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我已申请了\N来卫星六号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这门亲事\N由于是父母作主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才会这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的，米莱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你误会了\N请来舍下坐坐吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦...但是...\N我父亲会很开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你\N我什么也愿意做的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！         对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家不喜欢\N别勉强好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉，不要紧的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...算你走运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接住自己的眼镜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧，卡姆兰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能我的说服力不够呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，中尉\N你要小心才好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要知道\N米莱是母舰的褓姆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说你最先\N是德兹尔中将的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在却是\N希莉亚少将的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不觉得羞耻的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底给木马号\N走脱了多少次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是无能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你好好看着我的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底如何高明！      是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说你可以走的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你别太过份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的作战方法\N我会留心看的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙为何\N不脱下面罩的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听他额上有一处疤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有说是个美男子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总有一天\N我会脱下他的假面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些潜入\N巴达港多姆如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，仍未被发现呢！\N一切很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马亚，你待会回去后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就发暗号给希莉亚少将\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚在巴达内，知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是这种小事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别问那么多，照做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木村先生\N你已换了钱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里，是太空城市的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个令人觉得\N无重力的地带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这条电梯，约有三千米长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.35,0:11:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在下面\N就会有地心吸力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有重力的人造地面\N山，森林和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河流，与地球上的景色\N完全一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，亦有人造城市了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好，买了很多东西呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次吃的\N比以前丰富多了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样，阿姆罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们先回母舰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我过去那间书店看看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的作战成绩怎样？\N顺利吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔！跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还站着干什么？\N快进来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是下层阶级住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过在这里\N收集情报很方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会寄住在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你将它放在\N钢弹的记录线路里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些是我计算\N吉翁MS来参考的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.04,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种旧东西...爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来爸爸\N患了缺乏氧气病...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它很利害的\N钢弹的作战能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以增加数倍呢！\N快拿回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽快装在钢弹试试吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！但是爸爸你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还有很多研究课题...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迟些再联络你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，快回母舰去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，我在乡下\N见过妈妈呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，妈妈的事\N难道你不关心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...战争快结束了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们将可返回地球...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去吧！\N你现在已是个军人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，我何时\N批准你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在街上四处走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你，连出发也延迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！我想不到\N会突然出发的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你用钢弹\N去掩护白色基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是巴金先生吗？是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是卡姆兰\N请来帮忙的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.97,0:15:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！是他从首相处\N打电话给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要在领空以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是吉翁或联邦的战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也一样修理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在敌军正跟踪我们\N没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...这不要紧的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他们的高层人物\N很熟络的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，请你即管放心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢了，巴金先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，精神好点了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直也没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，那便好了\N乖孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加先生！      什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.84,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖孩子这句话\N请别再对我说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，是我不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了\N那不是木马号吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然这么傻走来这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便是流动船坞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔？是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说有信号来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是母舰驶出\N卫星六号的讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先确定位置\N然后开动引击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么木马号\N会这么快出来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明了！是流动船坞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说是巴金吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否那个在战争中\N赚大钱的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们舰队和敌人\N就成一直线了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即刻派出十二台多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们已经找到木马号吗？\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还派出了多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很大啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，原来是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...我的船坞...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特！我知卡姆兰\N不是这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部炮门打开吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！各单位注意\N立即展开攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉...请离开船坞\N远一点好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若这样下去\N我的船坞会完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在离开了...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是有裙的那一种！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个，再来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标是中间的战舰！\N攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姆沙舰被毁了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆呢？\N多姆到底在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可放松攻击啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.68,0:19:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流动船坞就是在附近吗？\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么吉翁会发现的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要停止战争的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.32,0:19:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些炮火是不可\N进入卫星领空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.05,0:20:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全灭？十二个多姆\N全没有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是在三分钟之内？是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一艘已受伤的战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将十二台多姆\N全部毁灭了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是怪物吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞斯巴尔来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚？你是想来笑我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞斯巴尔！         什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.61,0:20:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特\N我们不如先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.38,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！全舰注意\N返回卫星六号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.95,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我的船坞怎办？怎办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.03,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千万别开火\N有监察船在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫康斯肯部队停止攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若损坏了巡逻艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会演变成国际问题的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰检察官！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.81,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有勇气\N去叫他们停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过在联邦军战舰内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正有我的未婚妻\N米莱在内呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧的\N关于撕破封条的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸会想方法的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以借爸爸的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮你们留在卫星六号的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是这个意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要求我离开母舰，但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.65,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你会为我\N做什么事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.85,0:22:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以刚才不是说\N叫爸爸帮你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是不明白我的意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.36,0:22:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.10,0:22:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就是要我离开母舰\N留在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.53,0:22:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，你以前\N不会这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.00,0:22:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底要我做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.94,0:22:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没战争就好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，不是为了这个！
